<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=6053&amp;p=56629#p56629"><![CDATA[
Not always.<br /><br />Some mappers let you use multiple page sizes, such as MMC1, where you can use either 16K or 32K PRG pages.<br />Other mappers only let you use one size of page, such as MMC3, where all PRG pages are 8K in size.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=53">Dwedit</a> — Mon Feb 15, 2010 3:04 am</p><hr />
